---
title: "FFXIV Achievements"
layout: layouts/ffBase.njk
customcss: "/assets/css/ffxiv/ffxiv-achievements.css"
permalink: /shrines/finalfantasyxiv/achievements/
intro: |
  <p>
    My soft little Eorzean progress corner ♡ This page updates automatically and shows what achievement areas I’ve been active in lately, plus a few places I could focus on next.
  </p>
---

<section class="ffxiv-ach-page">
  <div class="ffxiv-bg-icons" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="bg-icon pom">✦</span>
    <span class="bg-icon star">★</span>
    <span class="bg-icon heart">♡</span>
    <span class="bg-icon flower">✿</span>
    <span class="bg-icon sparkle">✧</span>
  </div>

  <header class="ffxiv-ach-hero">
    <div class="ffxiv-ach-hero__mascot left" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="moogle-ball"></div>
      <div class="mascot-blob">🪽</div>
    </div>

    <div class="ffxiv-ach-hero__card">
      <div class="ffxiv-ach-hero__profile">
        {% if ffxivAchievements.portrait %}
          <img
            src="{{ ffxivAchievements.portrait }}"
            alt="{{ ffxivAchievements.characterName }}"
            class="ffxiv-ach-portrait"
          >
        {% endif %}

        <div class="ffxiv-ach-hero__info">
          <p class="ffxiv-ach-kicker">✨ moogle progress log ✨</p>
          <h1>{{ ffxivAchievements.characterName or "My Warrior of Light" }}</h1>
          <p class="ffxiv-ach-world">{{ ffxivAchievements.world or "Eorzea" }}</p>

          <p class="ffxiv-ach-desc">
            A dreamy little snapshot of my FFXIV achievement progress, updated automatically ♡
          </p>

          <div class="ffxiv-ach-links">
            <a href="{{ ffxivAchievements.achievementsUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Achievements ↗</a>
            <a href="{{ ffxivAchievements.categoryIndexUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Categories ↗</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ffxiv-ach-hero__mascot right" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="axolotl-face">
        <span>◕</span>
        <span>◕</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="ffxiv-ach-stats-grid">
    <article class="ffxiv-ach-stat-card">
      <span class="stat-icon">⭐</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Achievement Points</span>
      <strong class="stat-value">{{ ffxivAchievements.achievementPoints or "—" }}</strong>
    </article>

    <article class="ffxiv-ach-stat-card">
      <span class="stat-icon">📚</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Recent Achievements Tracked</span>
      <strong class="stat-value">
        {{ ffxivAchievements.recent.length if ffxivAchievements.recent else "—" }}
      </strong>
    </article>

    <article class="ffxiv-ach-stat-card">
      <span class="stat-icon">🕒</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Last Updated</span>
      <strong class="stat-value stat-value--small">
        {% if ffxivAchievements.updatedAt %}
          <time datetime="{{ ffxivAchievements.updatedAt }}">{{ ffxivAchievements.updatedAt }}</time>
        {% else %}
          —
        {% endif %}
      </strong>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="ffxiv-ach-card">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h2>Progress by Category</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">little pockets of progress i can work on next ♡</p>
    </div>

    {% if ffxivAchievements.categories and ffxivAchievements.categories.length %}
      <div class="ffxiv-cat-grid">
        {% for cat in ffxivAchievements.categories %}
          <article class="ffxiv-cat-card theme-{{ cat.theme }}">
            <div class="ffxiv-cat-top">
              <span class="ffxiv-cat-icon">{{ cat.icon or "✧" }}</span>
              <span class="ffxiv-tag tag-{{ cat.tag | replace(' ', '-') }}">{{ cat.tag }}</span>
            </div>

            <h3>
              <a href="{{ cat.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ cat.displayName or cat.name }}</a>
            </h3>

            <p class="ffxiv-cat-hint">{{ cat.hint }}</p>

            {% if cat.focusIdeas and cat.focusIdeas.length %}
              <ul class="ffxiv-cat-focus">
                {% for idea in cat.focusIdeas %}
                  <li>{{ idea }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
              </ul>
            {% endif %}

            <div class="ffxiv-cat-stats">
              <div>
                <span class="mini-label">Recent unlocks</span>
                <strong>{{ cat.recentCount or 0 }}</strong>
              </div>
            </div>

            {% if cat.recentTitles and cat.recentTitles.length %}
              <ul class="ffxiv-cat-recent">
                {% for title in cat.recentTitles %}
                  <li>{{ title }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
              </ul>
            {% else %}
              <p class="ffxiv-cat-empty">No recent achievements here just yet ♡</p>
            {% endif %}
          </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    {% else %}
      <p class="ffxiv-empty">No category data yet... kupo.</p>
    {% endif %}
  </section>

<section class="ffxiv-ach-card">
  <div class="section-head section-head--recent">
    <div>
      <h2>Recent Achievements</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">a tiny peek at my latest unlocks ♡</p>
    </div>

    <a
      class="ffxiv-more-link"
      href="{{ ffxivAchievements.achievementsUrl }}"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
    >
      view more on Lodestone ↗
    </a>
  </div>

  {% if ffxivAchievements.recent and ffxivAchievements.recent.length %}
    <div class="ffxiv-ach-list-wrap">
      <ul class="ffxiv-ach-list">
        {% for item in ffxivAchievements.recent %}
          {% if loop.index0 < 10 %}
            <li class="ffxiv-ach-item">
              <div class="ffxiv-ach-item__left">
                <span class="ffxiv-ach-badge">✦</span>
                <div class="ffxiv-ach-item__text">
                  {% if item.category %}
                    <small class="ffxiv-ach-category">{{ item.category }}</small>
                  {% endif %}

                  {% if item.url %}
                    <a href="{{ item.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ item.title }}</a>
                  {% else %}
                    <span>{{ item.title }}</span>
                  {% endif %}

                  {% if item.date %}
                    <small>{{ item.date }}</small>
                  {% endif %}
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  {% else %}
    <p class="ffxiv-empty">No recent achievements yet... time for a little adventure ♡</p>
  {% endif %}
</section>

    <aside class="ffxiv-ach-card ffxiv-ach-card--side">
      <h2>What I Could Work On Next</h2>

      <div class="suggest-block">
        <h3>Easy Wins</h3>
        {% if ffxivAchievements.suggestions.easyWins and ffxivAchievements.suggestions.easyWins.length %}
          <ul class="suggest-list">
            {% for item in ffxivAchievements.suggestions.easyWins %}
              <li>
                <span>{{ item.icon }} </span>
                <a href="{{ item.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ item.category }}</a>
                <small>{{ item.reason }}</small>

                {% if item.focusIdeas and item.focusIdeas.length %}
                  <small>
                    {{ item.focusIdeas[0] }}{% if item.focusIdeas[1] %} · {{ item.focusIdeas[1] }}{% endif %}
                  </small>
                {% endif %}
              </li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        {% else %}
          <p class="ffxiv-empty">Nothing obvious here yet ♡</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <div class="suggest-block">
        <h3>Quiet Lately</h3>
        {% if ffxivAchievements.suggestions.neglected and ffxivAchievements.suggestions.neglected.length %}
          <ul class="suggest-list">
            {% for item in ffxivAchievements.suggestions.neglected %}
              <li>
                <span>{{ item.icon }} </span>
                <a href="{{ item.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ item.category }}</a>
                <small>{{ item.reason }}</small>

                {% if item.focusIdeas and item.focusIdeas.length %}
                  <small>
                    {{ item.focusIdeas[0] }}{% if item.focusIdeas[1] %} · {{ item.focusIdeas[1] }}{% endif %}
                  </small>
                {% endif %}
              </li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        {% else %}
          <p class="ffxiv-empty">No especially quiet categories right now ♡</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <div class="suggest-block">
        <h3>Comfy Long-Term</h3>
        {% if ffxivAchievements.suggestions.active and ffxivAchievements.suggestions.active.length %}
          <ul class="suggest-list">
            {% for item in ffxivAchievements.suggestions.active %}
              <li>
                <span>{{ item.icon }} </span>
                <a href="{{ item.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ item.category }}</a>
                <small>{{ item.reason }}</small>

                {% if item.focusIdeas and item.focusIdeas.length %}
                  <small>
                    {{ item.focusIdeas[0] }}{% if item.focusIdeas[1] %} · {{ item.focusIdeas[1] }}{% endif %}
                  </small>
                {% endif %}
              </li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        {% else %}
          <p class="ffxiv-empty">Still gathering cosy long-term goals ♡</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>